やんばるエリア内での交通手段の満足度の理由: Very low frequency of busses and often delayed. Makes it really difficult to travel around the area but it gets you there in the end.
体験・サービス満足度の理由(やんばるエリア): Nice area, next time around I'm coming back to spend more time in Yanbaru National Park to go birdwatching. But I'll rent a car next time around. And I'll come in summer as there's more to do then.
推奨項目(やんばるエリア): Nature and the amazing beaches around.
改善点の内容(やんばるエリア): Difficulty of getting around without a rental car. If there are more busses going into nature that would be great as that is something that I now completely skipped due to availability of public transport.
